    • parse

      @Nonnull static <T extends GitRepositoryURL> T parse(@Nonnull String gitURL, @Nonnull Class<T> returnType) throws UnknownGitRepositoryURLTypeException
      Parsing URL address to subclass of GitRepositoryURL.
      Type Parameters:
      T - A subclass type which inherited from GitRepositoryURL.
      Parameters:
      gitURL - Git repository URL address.
      returnType - Which subclass of GitRepositoryURL will be return.
      Returns:
      An object of GitRepositoryURL subclass which defined return type from returnType.
      Throws:
      UnknownGitRepositoryURLTypeException - If parser can not find which subclass of GitRepositoryURL can be applied.
      ClassCastException - If returnType is set to GitRepositoryURL or the actual return type is not mentioned on returnType.
